show.description: Sarah is a cleaner who only has a high school education background. One day, she accidentally slept with the CEO, Mr. Leo. When Mr. Leo thinks that the person he slept with was Layla Gosling and decides to take responsibility for her, he finds out that his stepmother has already found him another wife on the day of the engagement. The new wife turns out to be Sarah. They are attracted to each other despite all the misunderstandings, and gradually fall in love with each other...
